eZ Online Editor extension 4.3.1 README

What is the eZ Online Editor extension?
=======================================

eZ publish Online Editor for XML fields.


eZ Online Editor version
========================

The current version of eZ Online Editor is 4.3.1.
You can find details about changes for this version in
doc/changelogs/CHANGELOG-4.3.1


